    public class DsMIB
extends Object
implements DsMIBMBean, Serializable
    The class is used for implementing the "DsMIB" group. The group is defined with the following oid: 1.3.6.1.2.1.66.

      • DsMIB

        public DsMIB(com.sun.management.snmp.agent.SnmpMib myMib)
